# RQ-53-10-01-024: Pitot Static Integration

## Requirement Statement
The nose cone shall integrate 3 pitot probes and 3 static ports with proper mounting and drainage.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Minimum 500mm separation between probes
- Heated pitot tubes (anti-ice)
- Drain holes prevent water accumulation
- Position error < 5 knots at all airspeeds

## Compliance Status
Design complete, wind tunnel testing planned

## Traceability
Parent: ATA 34 (Air Data System)
